    <title>使用Github Pages + Hexo搭建博客踩坑记录</title>
    <url>/2021/03/31/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Github-Pages-Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%B8%A9%E5%9D%91%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1>使用Github Pages + Hexo搭建博客踩坑记录</h1>
<h2 id="1-Hexo-d-无法部署到Github">1. Hexo d 无法部署到Github</h2>
<p>检查站点配置文件（不是主题配置文件）的deploy部分</p>
<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">repository:</span> <span class="string">git@github.com:Username/Username.github.io.git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">branch:</span> <span class="string">master</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="2-使用的主题报错-预览跟Demo差很多-无法使用">2. 使用的主题报错 / 预览跟Demo差很多 / 无法使用</h2>
<p>建议新手使用诸如<a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next">Next</a>、<a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid">Fluid</a>等有较多人维护，仍然活跃的主题，这类主题通常有完善的配置引导供你入门。</p>
<p>如果看英文有困难的话，这里贴两个<a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/3a05351a37dc?utm_campaign=maleskine&amp;utm_content=note&amp;utm_medium=seo_notes&amp;utm_source=recommendation">Next主题中文指引</a>、<a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="http://theme-next.iissnan.com/getting-started.html">Next文档</a>，别的主题找找也会有类似的文章。</p>
<h2 id="3-站点配置文件怎么写-各个关键字都是什么意思">3. 站点配置文件怎么写 / 各个关键字都是什么意思</h2>
<p>请参考Hexo官方文档，写的很清楚<a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/">Hexo</a></p>
<h2 id="4-Hexo-g报错failed-to-detect-version-info-cannot-read-property-replace-of-undefined">4. <code>Hexo g</code>报错<code>failed to detect version info, cannot read property 'replace' of undefined</code></h2>
<p>大概率是Github连接问题。将你的梯子调整成全局 / pac模式能解决</p>
<h2 id="5-Mac-用户安装-Node-js-报-EACESS-权限错误">5. Mac 用户安装 Node.js 报 EACESS 权限错误</h2>
<p>请参考<a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://docs.npmjs.com/resolving-eacces-permissions-errors-when-installing-packages-globally">npm官方文档</a>，强烈建议不要使用root覆盖安装</p>
<h2 id="6-找不到好看的主题">6. 找不到好看的主题</h2>
<p>这里推荐几个，主要是简约 / Material Design风格的</p>
<p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next">Next</a></p>
<p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid">Fluid</a></p>
<p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://github.com/Shen-Yu/hexo-theme-ayer">Ayer</a></p>
<p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://github.com/bolnh/hexo-theme-material">Material</a></p>
<p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://github.com/ppoffice/hexo-theme-icarus">ICARUS</a></p>
<h2 id="7-找不到好看的icon">7. 找不到好看的icon</h2>
<p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://fontawesome.com/">Font Awesome</a></p>
